OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1775589082
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman dies following 'assault' outside
OL,5,Cbar
OL,7,FA murder investigation has been
OL,8,Flaunched in Dorset after a man died
OL,9,Ffollowing an alleged assault in
OL,10,FBournemouth.
OL,12,FOfficers were called to reports of an
OL,13,Fincident outside My Bar in Charminster
OL,14,FRoad at around 3am on Monday April 6th.
OL,16,FA man aged in his 40s from
OL,17,FChristchurch was pronounced dead at
OL,18,Fthe scene. His family has been
OL,19,Finformed.
