PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1775589082
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman dies following 'assault' outside
OL,5,Cbar
OL,7,FTwo men from Bournemouth ` aged 37 and
OL,8,F46 ` and a 34-year-old man from Poole
OL,9,Fhave been arrested on suspicion of
OL,10,Fmurder.
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Nicky
OL,13,FJenkins, of Dorset Police's Major
OL,14,FCrime Investigation Team, said: "Our
OL,15,Fthoughts are with the family of the
OL,16,Fman who sadly died and a detailed
OL,17,Finvestigation is underway to establish
OL,18,Fwhat happened.
OL,26,@vD@aOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
