CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1775589082
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cman dies following 'assault' outside
OL,5,Cbar
OL,7,F"An extensive cordon has been put in
OL,8,Fplace and I would like to thank the
OL,9,Fpublic for their understanding while
OL,10,Fvital work at the scene is carried out.
OL,12,F"We know there were a number of people
OL,13,Fin the area at the time who may have
OL,14,Fwitnessed what happened and we would
OL,15,Fask them to please get in touch.
OL,17,F"I am also appealing to anyone who was
OL,18,Fdriving in the area and has dashcam
OL,19,Ffitted to their vehicle to please
OL,20,Fcheck it for any relevant footage.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
